OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,FRadio presenter Greg James has
OL,7,Fapologised following a backlash over
OL,8,Fnegative representations of disability
OL,9,Fin a promotional video for a new
OL,10,Fversion of Roald Dahl book The Twits.
OL,12,FIn the now-removed video, James and
OL,13,FChris Smith reportedly discuss how to
OL,14,Fmake the characters more revolting
OL,15,Fbefore James tells the illustrator to
OL,16,Fgive a character a glass eye to make
OL,17,Fher "more disgusting".
