OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,FAfter it was posted online, a
OL,7,Fspokesperson for the Royal National
OL,8,FInstitute Of Blind People (RNIB)
OL,9,Fresponded to say "there is nothing at
OL,10,Fall revolting about prosthetic eyes."
OL,12,FElsewhere, the chief executive of
OL,13,Fnational disability charity Sense,
OL,14,FRichard Kramer, said it was wrong for
OL,15,Fa video to be promoting a "negative
OL,16,Frepresentation of disability".
OL,18,FIn a post to his social media, James
OL,19,Fapologised and said: "Hello! Regarding
OL,20,Four new Twits story announcement video
OL,21,Ffrom this morning:
