OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,F"We are so sorry to have caused
OL,7,Foffence with the launch video.
OL,9,F"It was absolutely not our intention.
OL,10,FAnd we apologise unreservedly. It's
OL,11,Fnow gone.
OL,13,F"We understand that words matter and
OL,14,Fwe pride ourselves on championing and
OL,15,Fwelcoming everyone into the magical
OL,16,Fworld of children's books.
OL,18,F"We would never dream of deliberately
OL,19,Fsetting out to exclude anyone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
