OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,F"With the glass eye comment, we were
OL,7,Fattempting to pay homage to one of the
OL,8,FTwit's most famous pranks involving a
OL,9,Fglass of beer in order to remind
OL,10,Fpeople of Dahl's infamous terrible two.
OL,12,F"It's in no way a suggestion that this
OL,13,Fforms any part of the plot of the new
OL,14,Fstory nor was it our intention to
OL,15,Fsuggest that it was in any way
OL,16,Fdisgusting.
OL,18,F"It's unfortunate that the word
OL,19,Fdisgusting appears to be a direct
OL,20,Fcomment on that. That's an error on
OL,21,Four part.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
