OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,F"We are devastated that it's come
OL,7,Facross like this but completely
OL,8,Funderstand why there is anger."
OL,10,FJames said it was right for the video
OL,11,Fto be called out and said they were
OL,12,F"upset" about the mistake, but are
OL,13,F"still incredibly proud of this book".
OL,15,FMr Kramer said: "The video
OL,16,Fadvertisement for The Twits Next Door,
OL,17,Fpromoted on social media today, is
OL,18,Ftotally unacceptable and has rightly
OL,19,Fbeen removed by Puffin Books.
