OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,F"We remain concerned however that the
OL,7,Fbook, scheduled for release later in
OL,8,Fthe year, will contain a character
OL,9,Fwith a disability to show, in the
OL,10,Fwords of the video, how 'disgusting'
OL,11,Fthey are.
OL,13,F"It's 2024 and to be promoting such a
OL,14,Fnegative representation of disability
OL,15,Fis wrong. Disability is not a
OL,16,Fcharacter flaw.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
