OL,3,CGreg James 'so sorry' for video about
OL,4,Cnew Roald Dahl book after backlash
OL,6,F"Why would we want children to
OL,7,Fassociate a glass eye, or any
OL,8,Fprosthetic, with being disgusting?
OL,9,FWhat will children learn from that?
OL,10,FHow will that make disabled readers
OL,11,Ffeel?"
OL,13,FIn a post to X, the RNIB said: "When
OL,14,Fthere's positive representation of
OL,15,Fdisabilities in children's books,
OL,16,Fchildren with disabilities feel seen
OL,17,Fand heard, and their friends and
OL,18,Fclassmates treat everyone the same.
